		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: There is an instruction to reboot gb???</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />By using the /RESET line. The only way to make the bootstrap run again without powering off the GB would be to use the /RESET line on the cartridge port. This is useful for something like the EverDrive so that the game can startup in whichever mode is best, CGB or Mono GB for example.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
